Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Entity
  • public class Entity
extends Object
    Represents a player or enemy which can participate in a battle

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      private int health
      The current health of the Entity
      private int maxHealth
      The maximum possible health of the Entity
      private Move[] moveset
      All possible moves available to the Entity to use in battle.
      private String name
      The desired player-visible name of the Entity
      private int speed
      Speed of the Entity - can be used in battle to determine which Entity moves first
      private int status
      The current Entity's status.

      • speed

        private int speed
        Speed of the Entity - can be used in battle to determine which Entity moves first

      • status

        private int status
        The current Entity's status. 0 = no effect. 1 = poison, Entity's health will reduce by 20% every turn. 2 = confusion, every one of Entity's moves' accuracy is reduced by 30%. 3 = tired, Entity's speed is reduced by 50%.

      • moveset

        private Move[] moveset
        All possible moves available to the Entity to use in battle.
